Nigerian actress Halima Abubakar has called out gay men who are always deceiving women about their sexuality. The Nollywood actress disclosed this on Wednesday via her Instagram Stories while reacting to a report of a gay man who impregnated and dumped his fiancee for another man, She wrote, “I remember when I said many men do this and most of were busy insulting yourselves. Telling me BS. “Look tell us it’s not a big deal, stop hiding shit. We can sense it, stop lying to women.”